      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARK CINNAMON (2) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 20.49. Fair draw can see a good run and has a good record over this journey. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Looks the one to beat. NICKO KING (1) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish a nose away in second (20.88) behind Saint Mikey at this track. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Bold showing expected. POCKET TALK (4) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (19.92) in a NG at Goulburn. Solid record here winning two races. Great chance to atone. WINSOME WANDA (5) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
